creator: Landal GreenParks
descriptionHtml:
Download the app now and turn your holiday into a dream holiday.

ALL ACTIVITIES

Our Edutainement team organises all kinds of activities for young and old during the whole year. Want to have fun, learn something new and make new friends? In the app you can see all activities for this week and book them immediately.

IN THE RESORT

The app describes exactly what facilities are available at the resort. From the restaurants to the Supermarket and from the swimming pool to the Gift & Fashion Shop. Obviously the list also includes all the Educational Kids Academies. You also have the opening hours always with you.

AROUND THE RESORT

Discover the beautiful surroundings of Drenthe. Wonderful walking and cycling areas, cultural tips and theme parks for the whole family: there’s so much to do!

CULINARY

Enjoy delicious food in one of our restaurants. From a quick snack to a lovely three-course meal. Book a table in advance via the app! Then you can enjoy a carefree holiday.

MY STAY

Want to plan an activity in the resort or a day out? Save all your favourites in ‘My stay’.

CONTACT & INFORMATION

Questions? Get in contact with the Reception quick and easy via the app. Check important telephone numbers and directions to the resort. Get inspired by the app and have a wonderful holiday. Our staff is at your service.
descriptionShort: Get the most out of your stay with the Hof van Saksen app.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thanks for using the Landal GreenParks App! We are constantly working hard to improve the app and make it faster. Update to the latest version and enjoy the  newest and best version of the Landal GreenParks App.

title: Hof van Saksen App

creator: Landal GreenParks
descriptionHtml:
With the Hof van Saksen app, you can make the most of your stay! Discover our resort and activities, as well as all local tips. Add multiple reservations and go through the steps to make your vacation even more pleasant. Download the app now and enjoy a stress-free stay. Our staff is prepared for you!

START

Our new start screen serves as the starting point for both the preparation for your stay and the actual stay. All important information about your resort, from all facilities to an overview of your accommodations, can be found here. It is impossible to get lost in the resort with our map. For all inquiries, please contact our park reception.

RESORT

Take a look around the resort. Discover what activities are available at the resort and explore the surrounding area. Simply reserve a table at the restaurant or order sandwiches for the following morning.

RESERVATIONS

View all of your reservation's information in one place. Here you can see the booked accommodation, including everything that is present in your accommodation, which is very convenient! Simply use the app to add your remaining payment to your travel group. Using our simple booking overview, you can count down the days until your next stay.

PROFILE

In our new profile center, you can easily manage your preferences. You can change your password and select your desired language here. If you have any suggestions for us, please leave them in the feedback section. We make certain that the app continues to improve.
descriptionShort: Get the most out of your stay with the Hof van Saksen app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: It's time to celebrate! We've been hard at work recently on a new design for you. Our redesigned home screen ensures that you always see all of the important information for your stay at a glance. Less searching means more convenience! It is now also possible to display multiple reservations, allowing you to have even more holiday fun. Please update the app to the most recent version as soon as possible; we'd like to hear what you think. Greetings from the app team.

title: Hof van Saksen App

descriptionHtml:
